reviewText: Great to find an old time classic brought back to life. Fun to watch especially with family and kids.
This was way more than we expected to get and really great condition. Would recommend to anyone.
Bought as a gift, the recipient adored it.
Gave as a gift to my granddaughter
I have seen this dvd twice now and I love it. I will love to get this dvd soon.
